# contracts/ — curated by Eratosthenes

Data shape and interface contracts between specialists. When Champollion's output
is Nightingale's input, the shape of that data is a contract — changing it breaks
downstream work silently. This directory captures those contracts so both sides
can reference one source of truth.

Examples: `inventory-apps-json-schema.md`, `shared-cluster-overlap-fields.md`,
`dashboard-data-agents-json.md`.

Do not write to this directory. Submit via Protocol A — see common-prompt.md.
